12
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,760
We can only come to you.

13
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,480
Boss, I have no money.

14
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,680
No money?

15
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,840
No money

16
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,880
Look. You're a celebrity. You're a celebrity.

17
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:32,560
You're a superstar.

18
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,600
You make a lot of money.

19
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:36,850
You just need to be a little casual.

20
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,480
it'll be over.

21
