He paid so much back.

22
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,120
How much does he owe?

23
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:48,480
Is that all you owe me? Pay me back?

24
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,240
$100,000

25
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,620
Is 100,000 enough?

26
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,360
What do you think?

27
