Boss, the password.

29
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,440
What's the password?

30
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,460
I don't have money now.

31
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:11,720
But... But someone owes my dad money.

32
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:13,520
You have to give me time to ask for money.

33
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,400
Are you kidding me?

34
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,120
Ten days.

35
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:17,960
Ten days.

36
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,520
Ten days.

37
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,600
This is your last chance.

38
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,400
Don't fool me.

39
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:34,650
If you can't pay me back,

40
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:36,820
I have plenty of ways to mess with you.

41
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:37,890
Let's go.

42
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:55,400
You little...

43
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,720
Find a clean place next time.

44
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,520
Yes, boss.

45
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,080
You two.

46
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,160
Follow him.

47
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,600
Don't let him play any tricks again.

48
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,320
Yes.

49
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,360
Let's go.

50
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,560
They're over there.

51
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,159
Go!

52
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,920
You're haunting me.

53
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,680
I'll do my best.

54
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:03,920
Young man,

55
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,880
Look at us.

56
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,440
in Lincang.

57
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,540
Isn't the scenery beautiful?

58
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:15,040
The old tea mountain is very big.

59
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,780
It's hard to find someone.

60
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,640
I think

61
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,600
you'd better be prepared.

62
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,360
Are you alive?

63
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,400
What is it?

64
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:56,720
Sorry, bro.

65
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,740
The car broke down. I can't go.

66
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,960
But the old tea mountain is right ahead.

67
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:02,840
Just walk along the road.

68
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,880
Okay. How much is the fare?

69
