70
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,720
Just give me some.

71
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:10,620
Okay. Okay.

72
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,320
OK.

73
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,960
Customers of Linxiang District.

74
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:16,160
By the way, the chicken tastes good.

75
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,440
It came to me himself.

76
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,600
It's fate.

77
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,690
Take it with you.

78
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:21,900
Thank you. No need.

79
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,400
Okay, take care.

80
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:31,680
Murder! Murder!

81
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:34,090
I'm hanging up if you don't talk properly.

82
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,420
What are you doing?

83
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,320
Me?

84
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,280
