86
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,960
Party A calls 800 times a day.

87
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:42,920
A saliva song.

88
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,330
I don't want to write it.

89
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:46,159
Use AI for now.

90
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,340
Just do good deeds.

91
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,400
Save me.

92
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,760
Don't look for me recently.

93
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:50,840
Don't go to my house.

94
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:51,560
What's wrong?

95
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,690
