98
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,460
I'm hanging up.

99
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,760
No one is reliable.

100
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,159
Hello?

101
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,200
Hello?

102
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:50,960
Hello? Hello?

103
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:52,970
Sit outside.

104
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:06,090
